== Stochastic-process notation

The stochastic module provides filtration, martingale, predictability, stopping-time, and process helpers.

$Filtration_t$, $Mart(X)$, $adapted(X)$, $predictable(H)$, and $stopping(tau)$.

The filtration helper renders $FF(t)$.

The process helper renders $process(X, t)$.

The stopped-process helper renders $stopped(X, tau, t)$.
